th-1-tb-ssd-shadow-black%2F6559604.p\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow\"\u003e$649.99 on Best Buy\u003c/a\u003e makes it a much more attractive option. If you\u0026#39;ve been waiting for the time to buy one, now is probably the best time.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n    \n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
